NEWS wikipediatrend 
===============================================================================

version 0.3.1
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- option userAgent now is optional: the default is to send information on 
versions of R, wikipediatrend, curl as well as RCurl

- option requestFrom now is optional: the default is to not send the header

- wp_trend() now checks date inputs better for logical inconsistencies 
[see: wp_check_date_inputs()]